    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<div
  class="xl:h-[450px] container border-[#1F1F1F] border-2 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg flex-col"
>
  <h1 class="font-dm-sans font-semibold md:text-6xl text-4xl md:mb-10 mb-4">
    Thank You !
  </h1>
  <p
    class="font-dm-sans font-medium text-subheading max-w-[1058px] text-[#8C8C8C] text-center"
  >
    For considering DigitX for your digital needs. We look forward to connecting  with you and being part of your digital success!
  </p>
</div>
